      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542222962/RenderMan_CheckerBoard.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330597481&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542222962/RenderMan_CheckerBoard.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330597481&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"720\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542222995\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_CheckerBoard.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542222962\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"86c9a5ce-cd64-490a-a199-de1c540473a0\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><p><em>PxrChecker</em> computes a simple checkerboard pattern.</p><h3 id=\"PxrChecker-Parameters\"><span class=\"legacy-color-text-blue1\">Parameters</span></h3><h4 id=\"PxrChecker-ColorAandColorB\">Color A and Color B</h4><p>The two colors of the checkerboard squares.</p><h4 id=\"PxrChecker-Dimensions\">Dimensions</h4></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrChecker_color1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/